:'''Elaine:''' Well, I plan to look for some part-time jobs in the Overworld, hehe.
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} No more catching olms?
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_501029053-->
::'''Elaine:''' Yes... I can't even afford a drink at the Gathering Place with what I've earned from catching olms. Still, I've become a better cook of olm dishes...
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} What about your job at the mine?
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_501029055-->
::'''Elaine:''' I'll only be working part-time, so it won't affect my job at the mine. It doesn't take long to commute by cable car anyway. I'm mentally prepared for it.
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} Wouldn't it be tiring to travel to the Overworld daily?
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_501029057-->
::'''Elaine:''' I've considered the issue. It doesn't take long to commute by cable car and I'm mentally prepared for it.
:<!--Custom String Trigger: TalkSentence_501029058-->
:<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_501029058-->
:'''Elaine:''' Anyway, I'm just waiting for the Over and Underworlds to open up. I wonder what kind of job I'll be able to land. Oh, I should talk to Master Gertie before I leave.
:<!--Ends the current performance-->
:'''Elaine:''' *sigh* I haven't caught any olms today... Is it because I'm not patient enough?
:'''Elaine:''' ...Hey? When did you arrive? Sorry, I was catching olms and I didn't notice you were here.
:'''Elaine:''' But I don't think I can catch any olms any time soon... Do you want to chat with me?
